<span class="hl_good"><span class="hl_keyword">by</span> </span><a class="internal-link proof-step hl_good" href="/thy/trace/7/main/proof/transitivity/_"><span class="hl_keyword">contradiction</span> <span class="hl_comment">/* from formulas */</span></a><a class="internal-link remove-step" href="/thy/trace/7/main/proof/transitivity/_"></a><br/>
